**Why other files open fine but this one doesn't** — files without charts only have 4-5 XML parts written. This file has 75 because it has many copied charts (`copy13`, `copy14`, `copy17`, `copy18`), so every chart's colors/style XML also gets written without the declaration. The more charts a document has, the more broken parts accumulate.

